name: ELEFANCLUB 04
description:
An original illustration for collectors (5+) of Les Elefants Terribles.

"The king of comedy killing time for the punchline,
as a sirius dog light falls from the sky. Huh?

What have you done for me lately?
Watched my “Entertainment” yet?
Waved at the micro incandenza yet?
Caught Eleddha navel gazing on Canal Street?

We do live in overstimulated times…
vis-à-vis, AKA, both are excellent dances!

Poor Tracey, poor poor Tracey, covered in herpes.
This is your final monoxide handshake.
Long live your new flesh!
Silent. Silent.”

Rotring pen and markers on paper

By Guillaume Cornet and Only Child No Pets
Follow @elefants_tez on twitter
